CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 5, 1946, pg. 13, reads: "Celebrating - With all of her toys from Santa at her side, adorable Cecilia Thelma Champ, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Howard Champ, of Milwaukee Street, is about to take her bows...to the brand New Year...and you! - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of baby Cecilia Thelma Champ standing beside rocker with stuffed animals, in living room with tiled fireplace and small Christmas tree, in Champ home on Milwaukee Street
